{"id":363119,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":2,"day":14}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"204","ytitle":"","mtitle":"母子夜话","ftitle":"","authors":["宁宇"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁宇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没月没有星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满村挂黑灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有一窗明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传来捣米声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲门轻声问大妈:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“夜深人静已三更，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为何还不睡?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为何还劳累?”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大妈招呼我坐下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"端上一碗热香茶:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“孩子!明天做汤糰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃了汤糰不想家。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热泪滚眼眶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我叫声妈妈:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你和亲娘一样亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农业社就是我的家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冷了你送被，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收工你烧水；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干活手掌磨出泡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你心疼得要落泪……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寒风窗外巡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母子拉家常；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若不是鸡叫催人回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我和娘一夜话天亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1958.1.26。于七宝镇联明社"}]}